obmondo-lxd-backup-server (0.2.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Log startup as info
  * Fix service unit
  * Fix dependencies and control file
  * Exclude any dotfiles from build
  * Log directly to journald
  * Run as root to allow access to lxd socket
  * Log remote addr, add error handling for invalid JSON
  * Handle command with missing name
  * Properly handle older LXD versions
  * Capture stderr from exec
  * Signal completion in logs
  * Add idea for future improvement

